Danish

Tolkemønster giver mulighed for at evaluere sproggrammatik eller udtryk. Denne type mønster kommer under adfærdsmønster.
Dette mønster involverer implementering af en ekspressionsinterface,
som fortæller at fortolke en bestemt kontekst.
Dette mønster bruges i SQL-parsing, symbolbehandlingsmotor mv.

English

Interpreter pattern provides a way to evaluate language grammar or expression.
 This type of pattern comes under behavioral pattern.
 This pattern involves implementing an expression interface which tells to interpret a particular context.
 This pattern is used in SQL parsing, symbol processing engine etc.